                                                                                                               SPORT BRIEFS
                                          Nedved calls time on career
    Prague: Pavel Nedved is retiring from football, ending an 18-year career as a top class player despite numerous offers to continue. ldquo;I have decided not accept any of the offers I got recently and I end my career as a player for good, rdquo; the 37-year-old midfielder said on his website Wednesday. ldquo;I want to devote my entire time to the family, my wife and the children. rdquo;
